TopicTitle: Delta-V Maps and Wiki on KSPedia

Articles.Content:
Hello, I'm back "after a long winter" and got surprised by 1.9!

I'm currently in the process of updating all mods and wonder, has Squad changed KSPedia? Both Delta-V maps and Planet Wiki don't show up, even after updated...

4 hours ago, jlcarneiro said:

Hello, I'm back "after a long winter" and got surprised by 1.9!

I'm currently in the process of updating all mods and wonder, has Squad changed KSPedia? Both Delta-V maps and Planet Wiki don't show up, even after updated...  

Yes, depending on what features were used to create the KSPedia entries they will need to be redone or at least regenerated.  From the changelog, KSPedia entries now load on demand rather than being preloaded. Accordingly, there's an updated Part Tools.
